						<summary>

						<p>Slab set near the Mallikārjuna temple.</p>						

						<p>[Sōmēśvara I] (Date lost).</p>						

						<p>This badly mutilated inscription refers to the rule of Trailōkyamalla. Most of the letters are effaced; invocatory portion only is extant. It belongs to the 11th century A.D.</p>						

